title: Couple With Heart Man Man Light Skin Tone Medium Light Skin Tone
description: Represents a romantic couple composed of two men, with specific skin tone variations. It signifies love, partnership, and affection between two males.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this tender emoji depicts two men with light and medium-light skin tones embracing, with a prominent heart floating between them. The soft rounded edges and the warm, inviting glow of the heart, enhanced by Apple's signature realistic lighting, convey deep affection and connection. This emoji on Apple devices is a beautiful representation of romantic love and partnership, often used to express love, support, or celebrate relationships between men.
